-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104okl1665702907001.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/okl1665702907001.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/okl1665702907001.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"okl1665702907001\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Change Your Password\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<section class=\"section context\">\n<div class=\"div prereq\" id=\"okl1665702907001__topic_d40073e1_d40074e1_d40075e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"okl1665702907001__p_d40076e1_d40077e1_d40078e1\">You can change your password only for certain network paths. These paths must be specified in the [XLOGIN] section of your assignment file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"okl1665702907001__p_d40079e1_d40080e1_d40081e1\">Ensure that the Log On form displays when opening the path. This is determined by the path assignment in your assignment file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"okl1665702907001__p_d40082e1_d40083e1_d40084e1\">To change your password:</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"okl1665702907001__li_d20060e1_d20061e1_d20062e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Change Password</span> on the Log On form. This displays the Change Password form.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"okl1665702907001__li_d20063e1_d20064e1_d20065e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Enter the following information in the Change Password form:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"okl1665702907001__li_d20066e1_d20067e1_d20068e1\">Your current password in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Old Password</span> field\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"okl1665702907001__li_d20069e1_d20070e1_d20071e1\">Your new password in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">New Password</span> field\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"okl1665702907001__li_d20072e1_d20073e1_d20074e1\">Your new password in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Retype Password</span> field. This confirms that you have entered your password correctly\n </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"okl1665702907001__li_d20075e1_d20076e1_d20077e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">OK</span>.\n </span>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530620\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530620\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Change Your Password Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Change Your Password You can change your password only for certain network paths. These paths must be specified in the [XLOGIN] section of your assignment file. Ensure that the Log On form displays when opening the path. This is determined by the path assignment in your assignment file. To change your password: Click Change Password on the Log On form. This displays the Change Password form. Enter the following information in the Change Password form: Your current password in the Old Password field Your new password in the New Password field Your new password in the Retype Password field. This confirms that you have entered your password correctly Click OK . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}